Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶來了能代替我保護你的值得信賴的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鋼巴雷特登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 居然在這時候眼前一片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說已經到此為止了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.78,0:01:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還有..這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正是將這股力量解放之時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}優勝！！ 恭喜！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的希望所聚集起來的利劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全國大會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一直在腦內模擬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想站在大舞臺上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 弓道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我是馬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 想成為騎手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和全力奔跑的馬一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比任何人都更快地朝著終點飛奔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 很帥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 別那麼鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒到恭喜的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:02:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是第一戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是讓你抱著優勝的氣勢去拼搏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想讓維也納的努力白費麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那高高在上的想法是什麼啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 和奏你的沙球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 去面對強大的敵人吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我今天身體稍微有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs74\c&H000000&\blur2\shad5\3c&HB8B8C4&\fad(640,0)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\b0\i1\4c&H606060&\pos(357,364)}捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs74\c&H000000&\blur2\shad5\3c&HB8B8C4&\fad(640,0)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\b0\i1\4c&H606060&\pos(281,470)}無法捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是玩過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來夏喜歡祭典嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭典？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 田中開始打羽毛球的契機是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別打馬虎眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白浜坂高中的 田中大智君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}（請到指定的區域去準備）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奮起 一口氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}（這是江戶時代一起衝鋒的口號）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大智 準備好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}（以必死的決心喝一杯營養飲料）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請慢慢享用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 有粉色的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉色 只有在這裡的這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色不也蠻好的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠻快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那請給我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:04:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 能幫我再倒一杯茶麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我來做晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 請在這邊付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽結束 和田勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前八強的話已經很厲害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是前四強的話就能在全日本大會裡出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中 好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那順便買綠茶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃...請走好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微幫我拿下包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是做了下腦內模擬練習而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著記憶還比較清楚的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不想再輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春香姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中是什麼時候開始打羽毛球的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多小學三年級的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在社團開始打羽毛球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大智也立刻說他也要打然後想要自己的球拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是小學的時候開始打的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼沒去羽毛球更流行的高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白高的話可以自行車就能上下學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前部員也不少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憧憬的選手也是我們學校出身...之類的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說是因為那個選手蔡開始打羽毛球的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說別打馬虎眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是夏天也不要讓身體冷下來在賣了熱的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 紗羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近有點沒精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 海水好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是志保喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久違地受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別告訴紗羽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動不動就說我已經不年輕了那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一年不如一年了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們感情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便放那裡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿身大汗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要泡個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了 稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是白高畢業的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏的學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候這一帶不是上白高就是鐮高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是和奏的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真昼學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我高一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是高倉學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高倉直子現在是教頭老師了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你完整得複製一張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是合唱部的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大賽中取得優勝時的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒從媽媽哪裡聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒對那孩子說過生病的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那孩子正在準備考試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 稍等 對不起 那個我來做就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要我來做飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒...那麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很閑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會 很忙的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說媽媽昏倒嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都太誇張了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次也很快就能出院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去換個抹布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 要保重身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是和奏一起寫歌的話說不定就能好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想聽聽和奏的點子呀意見什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有做這種事的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就要考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一起唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繃得太緊的話實力會發揮不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為是因為誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被生氣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起寫歌的話說不定就好起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 認真教我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是好的範例吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候經常這樣一起唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然學習也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是考完試後音樂也要繼續哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願讓音樂時刻伴隨和奏左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願和奏不忘摯愛音樂的初心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能通過考試就沒有意義了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰閃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那週末靠你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話從星期一開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 這種事就是相互關照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野家的叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰又不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算週一下田去幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.56,0:12:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀子是上班族不能突然請假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過可能需要兩三天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己沒關係麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是小孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚飯要不要叫壽司呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:12:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把房間裡的鋼琴處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正已經用不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給其他真正喜歡音樂的人用的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想媽媽也會覺得高興的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CD不大的話自己也可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他不要的東西也一起收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要放張床在空出來的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我明天打電話問問看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關東地區
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早晨開始雲層增厚擴張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:14:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前有強低氣壓自小笠原群島沿海緩慢北上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受其影響 今天白天到傍晚天氣開始惡劣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,補習結束的晚的話 帶上雨衣會比較好喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風好像也會變大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是今天會來拿鋼琴之類的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我都分得很容易明白的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金魚啦 金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:14:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鯨魚啦 鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那折中一下 就當它是海豚先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海豚先生在唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我三點半也出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事就給我打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過叔叔家手機信號不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道遠野的號碼不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚飯可以叫壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說別擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後有社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便的話要一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了慶祝大智擠進八強要舉辦派對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天想趕在下雨之前買好東西回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等會有羽毛球賽的討論會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中請客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思呢 今天有點小忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 可是蛋糕也買了和奏的份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超大的草莓的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去吃一下蛋糕也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然沒什麼精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不喜歡草莓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是我被嫌煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個倒是有點可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銅鑼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銅鑼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銅—鑼—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說了幫我把雨衣拿出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...抱歉 馬上幫你拿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的東西起碼自己準備好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准考證帶了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有忘了什麼別的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走好啊 加油喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銅鑼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.59,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 別忘帶了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西又無所謂的說...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會淋濕的趕快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今以後想跟女兒一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟和奏一起往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些充實的時光 荒廢的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜悅的時光 傷感的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的歌曲 跟和奏一起的話感覺能創作出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 歌是傳達愛的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後和奏也教會了我重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要傳達給和奏的情感化作了歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能一起唱出那首歌...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 如果能夠聽到和奏的歌聲...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人生...就是一百分滿分了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能說出口...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我出發了」...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「對不起」...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有「謝謝」...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也沒辦法一起唱歌了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.17,0:21:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏！！不可以！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏 你覺得對我們來說首先需要的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.13,0:23:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}第六話 歡笑 想念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 和奏 接下來有時間嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OPJ-------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.50,0:00:35.00,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}胸の奥が高鳴る
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.63,0:00:38.47,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}熱い声に気付いたら
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.72,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}スタートラインは
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.72,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}君の目の前にある
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.97,0:00:46.35,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}まだ見えない道でも
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.10,0:00:49.85,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}走り始めればいいさ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.89,0:00:52.06,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}諦めるよりも
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.73,0:00:55.19,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}素敵だと思わない？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.48,0:01:00.28,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}いつも不安はすぐ傍で
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.32,0:01:06.20,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}駆け出す思いを 締め付けるけれど
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.33,0:01:09.50,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}今を越えて 歩き出す
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.54,0:01:12.25,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}未知なる道に光を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.29,0:01:15.21,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}初めてを 繰り返し
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.25,0:01:17.84,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}掴み取れ 明日を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.88,0:01:20.97,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}さっさと友達が無限の
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.01,0:01:23.64,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}夢抱きしめ 進むのさ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.72,0:01:29.56,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}輝いてる自分を信じていい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.64,0:01:32.35,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}立ち上がる力に
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.44,0:01:35.19,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}盛大の愛を込めて
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.27,0:01:37.94,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}思うまま 旅立とう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.98,0:01:43.95,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}新しい世界の中へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OPC-------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.50,0:00:35.00,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}胸口傳出響亮的聲響
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.63,0:00:38.47,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}希望有誰能夠注意到這熱忱的聲音
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}人生的Start Line
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}無時無刻都會出現在你的眼前
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.97,0:00:46.35,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}即使是看不到盡頭的道路
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.10,0:00:49.85,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}只要踏出第一步就是前進
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.89,0:00:52.06,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}比起直接放棄
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.73,0:00:55.19,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}不覺得這樣更好嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.48,0:01:00.28,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}不安總是徘徊在我們的身旁
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.32,0:01:06.20,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}將這份鼓動的心情 關閉在深處的抽屜裡
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.33,0:01:09.50,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}讓我們邁出腳步越過現在
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.54,0:01:12.25,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}照亮那條未知的道路
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.29,0:01:15.21,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}不斷重複著將終點轉變為起點
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.25,0:01:17.84,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}用我們的雙手抓住未來
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.88,0:01:20.97,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}趕快集結起夥伴
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.01,0:01:23.64,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}擁抱無限的夢想 向前推進
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.72,0:01:29.56,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}鼓起勇氣相信閃耀著的自己吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.64,0:01:32.35,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}將盛大的愛灌注進乾涸的心靈
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.44,0:01:35.19,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}給再次站起來的力量
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.27,0:01:37.94,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}就讓我們任著性子去旅行吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.98,0:01:43.95,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}讓我們換乘進入新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------EDJ-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:14.13,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}晴れた日 雨の日でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:21.14,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}皆がいればいつも 笑顔になれた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:30.40,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}記憶の彼方まで 思い出したり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:34.57,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}揺蕩う声 耳澄まそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:40.87,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}さぁ 手を差し伸べられて輪の中へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:44.54,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}一人じゃない空間で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:48.84,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}夢中になってる時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:54.76,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}心地良い風が吹いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:23:01.93,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}笑ったり 泣いたり 歌ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:07.52,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}閉じていたこころも開いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:14.36,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}思い出のフレーズ 口ずさむ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:19.74,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}奏でよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------EDC-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:14.13,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}無論是放晴的日子 還是下雨的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:21.14,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}有大家陪伴在身邊的話 無論何時都能保持笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:30.40,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}即使在記憶的最深處 也要回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:34.57,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}這搖蕩的聲音 讓我們傾耳聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:38.91,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}來嘛 讓我們一起伸出雙手鏈接起圓環
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:44.54,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}製造出不是一個人的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.54,0:22:48.84,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}享受著這夢幻般的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:54.76,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}一股清風吹起平靜了心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:23:01.93,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}歡笑了 哭泣了 勇敢的歌唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:07.52,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}曾經緊閉著的心房也悄然敞開了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:14.36,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}充滿回憶的旋律 輕聲吟唱著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:19.74,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1}奏響吧
